Question: Does the sailboat that is to the right of the boat look white?

Reference Answer: Yes, the sailboat is white.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n195925.jpg

Program:

```
 Does A <planar pos> B look <attr>?
Program:
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='boat')
IMAGE0=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='sailboat')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the sailboat?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'white' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
